Hom(\mathbb{Z}^r \oplus_i \mathbb{Z}/d_i, \mathbb{Z}) \simeq Hom(\mathbb{Z}^r, \mathbb{Z}) \oplus_i Hom(\mathbb{Z}/d_i, \mathbb{Z}) \simeq \mathbb{Z}^r
